articles.title: Dusty Hill, bearded bassist of blues trio ZZ Top, dies at age 72 - ABC News
articles.description: Band mates of the long-serving bassist of the iconic American blues trio announce Hill's death, saying the "monumental bottom to the 'Top'" will be missed.
articles.content:
ZZ Top bassist Dusty Hill, one of the Texas blues rock trio's bearded figures, has died at his Houston home, the band announced. He was 72.
  • No cause of death has been given for Hill
